
Ranger Help for: enemy pinniped
===============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing pinniped means your Ranger specializes against seals, sea lions,
walruses, and similar flippered shoreline or arctic creatures.

This is a specialized beach and arctic choice. It matters most around
coasts, ice, cold seas, and seal-haunted shores.

COMMAND:
  setenemy pinniped

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
